ce/Pope_Francis\", \"score\": 0.9978569052351401, \"rank\": 0.002100412840285212, \"text\": \"Francis\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19546\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pope_Francis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pope_Francis\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"kids' songs\", \"from\": 3515, \"to\": 3526}, {\"ngram\": \"the boat\", \"from\": 3530, \"to\": 3538}, {\"ngram\": \"our heads\", \"from\": 3557, \"to\": 3566}]}, {\"sentence\": \"American marathon runner Clayton Young had his daughters help him train by yelling power phrases every time he went by through a grass loop section on his training route.\", \"from\": 3616, \"to\": 3786, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3616, \"end\": 3624, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999218025594419, \"rank\": 7.81942203517458e-05, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his daughters\", \"from\": 3659, \"to\": 3672}, {\"ngram\": \"power phrases\", \"from\": 3699, \"to\": 3712}, {\"ngram\": \"a grass loop section\", \"from\": 3743, \"to\": 3763}, {\"ngram\": \"his training route\", \"from\": 3767, \"to\": 3785}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When he clinched his spot at the Olympic trials earlier this year, they were among the first to hug and congratulate him at the finish line.\", \"from\": 3787, \"to\": 3927, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his spot\", \"from\": 3804, \"to\": 3812}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic trials\", \"from\": 3816, \"to\": 3834}, {\"ngram\": \"hug\", \"from\": 3883, \"to\": 3886}, {\"ngram\": \"the finish line\", \"from\": 3911, \"to\": 3926}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Kids take a lot of physical effort and exertion,\\\" Young told The Associated Press.\", \"from\": 3929, \"to\": 4012, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Kids\", \"fro